    <h2 {...{
      "id": "circlecalculatorradius-solvefor"
    }}><inlineCode parentName="h2">{`circleCalculator(radius, solveFor)`}</inlineCode></h2>
    <p>{`In order to implement the various circle-related formulas in our code with Mathium, we must call the function using Mathium's API, as such:`}</p>
