When applying the formula for circumference, the result would be the following:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`C = 2πr = 2π(423.89)
C = 2663.38
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`When used in our code, we can make it look like the following:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-ts"
